Jeanette Chabalala, News24Man killed after car crashes into tree. (Supplied) Multimedia &nbsp; &nbsp; User Galleries &nbsp; &nbsp; News in Pictures Send us your pictures &nbsp; &nbsp; Send us your stories Johannesburg &ndash; A man was killed on Saturday evening after he lost control of his vehicle and smashed into a tree at the corner of Blandford Road and Hyperion Drive in Olivedale , Gauteng paramedics said. &nbsp;ER24 spokesperson Chitra Bodasing said when they arrived on scene they found the man in the vehicle. &nbsp;He was declared dead on scene.Bodasing said authorities were on scene for further investigation. &nbsp;24.com encourages commentary submitted via MyNews24. Contributions of 200 words or more will be considered for publication.